title: GEORGE BURNS and GRACIE ALLEN SHOW -- Gracie Pawns Her Ring
description:
This came right after the 1955 Christmas episode, which is when of two from 
this sixth year that I don't have.  In that one George gave Gracie a diamond ring 
as a present. Guess what she foolishly does in this episode ?

Semi-regulars include Peter Brocco as Peter, the hotel waiter and 
Ronnie's friend Jim Boardman (played by a lesser-known actor in several shows).
